        {
            "title": "〈熱門股〉GIS-KY轉型半導體光學領航 周漲46％創波段高點",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">觸控面板廠 GIS-KY(6456-TW) 本周股價表現強勁，受到轉型半導體、Micro LED、VR 等高端領域題材激勵，17 日股價收 77.6 元，周漲幅達 46.97％，創近期波段高點，周成交量 141328 張。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">GIS-KY 正積極由傳統觸控顯示模組轉向半導體光學領域，布局涵蓋 Micro LED 與光波導及車用顯示等多項高階應用。透過半導體製程打造奈米級光學元件，公司已導入奈米壓印與晶圓級鍵合設備，藉此強化未來競爭力。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-93fe1d3c-9257-3ab2-bd3d-d6e95d938cea-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">海外產能布局方面，越南新廠自去年第三季底動工後進度符合預期，預計將在今年第三季完工。若後續客戶驗證進展順利，目標於今年底正式導入量產並開始營運出貨。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\" GIS-KY(日 K 線圖\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"500\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/L560_B3mV68ay4KjuYTDyg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgyOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/cnyes_hk_559/56d20c07810c065e07858d4824ff782c\" width=\"580\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:580px\"> GIS-KY(日 K 線圖</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap read-more-vendor break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span>更多鉅亨報導</span><br/>•<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"GIS-KY遭列注意股 自結3月稅後虧損4600萬元 EPS -0.14元\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:GIS-KY遭列注意股 自結3月稅後虧損4600萬元 EPS -0.14元;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6422361?utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_campaign=relate\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">GIS-KY遭列注意股 自結3月稅後虧損4600萬元 EPS -0.14元</a><br/>•<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"GIS-KY Q1營收拚成長 斥資50億元強攻光學轉型放眼後年\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:GIS-KY Q1營收拚成長 斥資50億元強攻光學轉型放眼後年;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6392204?utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_campaign=relate\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">GIS-KY Q1營收拚成長 斥資50億元強攻光學轉型放眼後年</a></p></div>",
